data.name: label9.Text
data.value: "T.A.C.O. is 100% free, and always will be." -McNubblet Since this project has been abandoned I've decided to take it over so please consider a donation of ISK to Captain Crump KingSlayer if you use T.A.C.O. regularly. Any donations will be greatly appreciated :)

data.name: label24.Text
data.value: You can enable and disable the feature on a per character basis through the map context menu. It works by alerting you when combat for an enabled character is not detected for 30 seconds after being in combat.

data.name: label22.Text
data.value:
T.A.C.O. is still BETA software, it does contain bugs unfortunately.
If you'd like to see a feature added or have a suggestion to make TACO better, please let me know.
Also, if you find a bug, please let me know about it. If you could provide a few details about how I can reproduce the bug and send me your config, it would make fixing it much easier.
Config files can be zipped and attached to a forum PM.
